                                INTRODUCTION
                                ------------

This simple program has been written in C and compiled with DICE (Free
Version). It is my first attempt to write a C program for Amiga 
(see @{"Author" link "author" 0} for more informations...). 
It's an improved porting from my Unix Version (see @{"History" link "history" 0}).
However,it has been speeded up on Amiga, due to optimized code. This is
version 1.31. You can use it on BINARY files too...

                     REMEBER, THIS IS A BETA VERSION!
          I HAVE NO RESPONSABILITY ABOUT DAMAGES AT YOUR SYSTEM.

SCrypter is very useful if used with DOPUS,assigning it to a button.

@endnode

